            <p>We are not responsible for what you write about them, so please make sure that you do not offend any of your friends. Friendship is important in everyone's life.</p>
            
            <p>But if you don't care about this friendship anymore we suggest you remove this person from your facebook instead of offending them on the GoLeak network.</p>

            <p>Offensives messages will be reviewed by our team and can be removed.</p>
            
